<p>I&#8217;m almost ashamed of how little reading I do after reading this.  Pretty much all of my reading is done on the bus to and from school.  Thanks for the inspiration.  Maybe in a month or two I will make it my goal to read 10 books in 30 days.  (February is the <a href="http://www.rpmchallenge.com/" rel="nofollow">RPM Challenge</a>, and I still haven&#8217;t decided whether I want to participate in that.)</p>

